title: German Freak ASMR - Eating sounds made in Germany
description:
ASMR eating no talking channel about delicious German food! Let me tell you my story why I'm doing ASMR eating no talking!

I was searching for some videos about "hypnosis" and "meditation". One day there appeared a video suggestion at the YouTube video sidebar "ASMR..." with a beautiful German Russian girl called "Pelagea". I clicked and watched the video. It was so damn relaxing. I could't stop watching her videos. They brought to sleep. 

Then I checked YouTube for more ASMR videos. I found "WillsonEatsASMR" and "Binaural Eats ASMR". Also super relaxing videos with eating sounds. I love these guys. Inspired by them I decided to make videos for the ASMR community with German food!
